How to use VS Code connected (or not) to HiperGator

(~under construction~)

Download VS Code:
https://code.visualstudio.com/download

Install VS Code:
https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/setup/setup-overview

Make VS Code SSH to HPG:
https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/remote/ssh

Fix the asking for password indefinitely:
https://stackoverflow.com/questions/69277631/2fa-with-vs-code-remote-ssh

First login to hipergator in your local terminal and the on VSCode.

Install any extensions (like Jupyter) by going to the Extensions icon on the left.
Source Control (also on the left) allow you to use git commands.
